{"tid":813692,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我呢一生犯左無數既錯，生係富察家，天性不愛拘束","createTime":"2018-09-10T15:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T16:31:14.000Z","uid":58316,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ecef08d0108b1825dbf8872bc182a959d9493df3","tid":813692,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:55:47.000Z","msg":"偏偏嫁入皇室<br />\n成為大清皇后<br />\n此為一錯<br />\n成為六宮典範<br />\n聽從體統規矩<br />\n依舊留戀過去<br />\n大夢不醒<br />\n此為一錯<br />\n失去真正既自己<br />\n做左扯綫木偶<br />\n偏偏貪戀兒女情長<br />\n期望得到皇上既愛<br />\n此為一錯<br />\n生下永璉，永琮<br />\n但係根本無力保護<br />\n以致痛失愛子<br />\n實在枉為人母<br />\n此為一錯<br />\n天下本就無情<br />\n禮教深嚴<br />\n不可逾越<br />\n但妄想君皇有情<br />\n不知人心險惡<br />\n天道殘忍<br />\n一而再再而三咁遭到背叛<br />\n一步錯<br />\n步步錯<br />\n皇上<br />\n你講得冇錯<br />\n我唔係一個好皇后<br />\n對唔住呀<br />\n瓔珞<br />\n應承要等你回宮<br />\n可惜我等唔到喇<br />\n不過<br />\n你要為我高興<br />\n從今以後<br />\n我唔再做皇后<br />\n只做富察容音<br />\n我<br />\n只係<br />\n富察容音"},{"pid":"920701cb910540fb9644ce008faf50a7a7fa7ecf","tid":813692,"uid":48277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:58:34.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"561a08d1f320bc35f60a52480b032679a284ce28","tid":813692,"uid":53577,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T16:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/000116_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F000116_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=90dac198&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d4cee0107bec242fc2dcaf6276316ee830988d5","tid":813692,"uid":12075,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"561a08d1f320bc35f60a52480b032679a284ce28","tid":813692,"uid":53577,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T16:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/000116_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eserv